---

---

<section class="developer" id="developer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="developer__inner">
      <div class="developer__text">
        <span class="section-label">Developer</span>
        <h2>Dibangun Oleh Yang Berpengalaman</h2>
        <p>
          Haventerra dikembangkan oleh PT Sentral Properti Indonesia — developer
          yang sudah membangun 8 kawasan hunian sejak 2013. Zero delay handover,
          sertifikat tepat waktu, dan after-sales yang selalu responsif.
        </p>
        <div class="developer__certs">
          <span class="developer__cert">✓ REI Member</span>
          <span class="developer__cert">✓ ISO 9001:2015</span>
          <span class="developer__cert">✓ Green Building</span>
          <span class="developer__cert">✓ Partner 9 Bank</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="developer__stats">
        <div class="developer__stat">
          <div class="developer__stat-num">8</div>
          <div class="developer__stat-label">Kawasan Hunian</div>
        </div>
        <div class="developer__stat">
          <div class="developer__stat-num">12</div>
          <div class="developer__stat-label">Tahun Pengalaman</div>
        </div>
        <div class="developer__stat">
          <div class="developer__stat-num">4.500+</div>
          <div class="developer__stat-label">Unit Terbangun</div>
        </div>
        <div class="developer__stat">
          <div class="developer__stat-num">0</div>
          <div class="developer__stat-label">Delay Handover</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .developer {
    background: var(--color-dark-band);
    padding: var(--section-py) 0;
  }
  .developer__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .developer__text .section-label {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }
  .developer__text h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    line-height: 1.18;
  }
  .developer__text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .developer__certs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .developer__cert {
    padding: 7px 15px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    border-radius: var(--rounded-full);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .developer__stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px 48px;
  }
  .developer__stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .developer__stat-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .developer__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>
